Executive Profile
Thomas F. Frist IIIFounder and Managing Principal, Frist Capital, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 7 Board Members in 7 different organizations across 9 different industries.See Board Relationships49--
Background

		Mr. Thomas F. Frist, III, also known as Tommy, Founded Frist Capital, LLC and has been its Managing Principal since 1994. Mr. Frist served as a Principal at Frist Capital, LLC. He was the co-founder of FS Partners, LLC. He worked at Rainwater, Inc. He has been a Director of HCA Holdings, Inc. since 2006.  He has been an Independent Director at VeriSign, Inc. since December 3, 2015. He serves as a Director of VH Holdings Inc., GPCH-GP, Inc., Brookwood Medical Center of ... Gulfport, Inc., EP Health, LLC, HCA Realty, Inc., and Montgomery Regional Hospital, Inc. He served as an Independent Director of Science Applications International Corporation since September 27, 2013 until June 7, 2017. He served as a Director of Leidos Holdings, Inc. from 2009 to September 27, 2013. He served as a Director of Leidos, Inc. until September 2013. He was a Director of Women's and Children's Hospital, Inc. He served as a Director of Triad Healthcare Corporation from 1999 to October 31, 2006. He holds a BA from Princeton University in 1991 and an MBA degree from Harvard Business School in 1997.Read Full Background




